image_analysis.description: A high-angle, eye-level photograph of the facade of a limestone townhouse or mansion. The building features ornate architectural details including arched windows on the ground floor, a central arched wooden doorway with a lit lantern hanging above it, and a second-story balcony with an intricate black wrought-iron railing. Two large deciduous trees with green leaves flank the central entrance, their trunks partially obscuring the view of the building's windows. The building to the left is made of light-colored brick.
